Insert a Sales Summary (Doughnut Chart)
Select an empty cell.
Go to Insert > Chart > Doughnut Chart.
Add data manually for:
Actual Sales
Target Sales.
Use different colors for actual vs. target sales.
Create a City-wise Sales (Line Chart)
Select the City and Total Sales columns.
Insert > Line Chart.
Adjust X-axis for city names.
Apply Data Labels to highlight peak sales.
Create a State-wise Sales (Map Chart)
Select the State and Total Sales columns.
Insert > Map Chart.
Ensure state names match Excelâ€™s mapping.
Apply gradient color scaling.
Create a Product-wise Sales (Bar Chart)
Select Product Category and Units Sold.
Insert > Bar Chart > Horizontal Bar Chart.
Sort products in descending order.
